e: ￹`O~ `safa~ `iso~ `ko~ `mi~`heca~`an~ `ako~.￺I am younger than you.￻我年齡比你小
￹`O~ `safa~ `ako~ `konini~.￺1. This is my younger brother / sister.  2. This is my younger cousin.￻1. 這是我的弟弟或妹妹  2. 這是我的表弟妹
￹`Ma~`safa~ `nira~ `kako~.￺He has excelled over me.￻他優於我
￹`Aka~ `pala~`safa~`en~ `cingra~.￺Don't put down someone (of standing).￻不要看輕他，不要藐視他
￹`Misa~`fa~ `cingra~ `to~ `fana'~ `ako~.￺He put down my ability.￻他藐視我的能力
